
<html class="home">
<head>
    <%- include("includes/head") %>
    <% headUrl = "https://info.chrispricemusic.net/lessons"%>
    <% headName = "Chris Price â€¢ Music & Media | Lessons" %>
    <title><%= headName %></title>

    <!-- SEO Meta -->
    <meta name="description" content="Original music, sound design, and multimedia content by Chris Price. Explore compositions, media projects, and creative collaborations.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Chris Price, music composer, media producer, sound designer, audio, original music, film score, video, content creator">
    <meta name="author" content="Chris Price">
    

    <!-- Open Graph (Facebook, LinkedIn, Discord) -->
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= headName %>">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Explore the work of Chris Price: composer, sound designer, and media creator. Hear original scores and view featured media projects.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://info.chrispricemusic.net/img/chris.jpg">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= headUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= headName %>">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Music and multimedia content by Chris Price. Discover original compositions and sound design projects.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://info.chrispricemusic.net/img/chris.jpg">

    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= headUrl %>">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include("includes/header", {header: "music"}) %>
    </header>
    <main class="main">
        <% if(typeof error !== "undefined") { %>
            <br>
            <h1 style="text-align: center; padding: 8px; border: solid 2px #F00; border-radius: 8px;"><%= error %></h1>
            <br>
        <% } %>
        <br>
        <h1 style="text-align: center;">Lessons</h1>
        <br>
        <div style="margin: 16px">
            <p>Music theory, composition, and arrangement lessons are offered by Chris Price to continue your music journey. Each lesson is 1 on 1, either in person, or online. Each session is $35. A roadmap of your journey will be made based on where you are and where you want to be. You'll learn several important skills for being a musician, including how to write, how to format parts, how to create quiality renderings, and how to get your music performed.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <form method="POST" action="/lessons">
            <h2>Music Lesson Inquiry</h2>

            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="First and Last Name" required>

            <label for="country_state">Country/State</label>
            <input type="text" id="country_state" name="country_state" placeholder="Washington" required>

            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@email.com" required>

            <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) - 555 - 5555" required>

            <label for="year">Year in School</label>
            <input type="text" id="year" name="year" placeholder="College Freshman/Highschool Senior" required>

            <label for="message">Tell us about your music journey</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Share your background, goals, and experience in music..." required></textarea>

            <br>
            <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6Lchm2ErAAAAAGGXkJ9ane8BFngVnsa8tXF_PofO"></div>
            <br>
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <%- include("includes/footer") %>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
